&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 6 Rotational Occupational Therapist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£37,638 - £44,780 per annum incl. HCAS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chelsea and Westminster Hospital&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has come up for for an Occupational Therapist to join our rotational band 6 programe within the Therapy Service at Chelsea and Westminster Hospital NHS Foundation trust. The post will rotate through a wide variety of specialties and clinical settings and allow for supported learning, development of skills and professional development in both in and outpatient enviroments .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The rotations include 8 months in Medical Rehabilitation, Frailty and older adults. Emergency and acute assessment , Orthopedics, Neurology, Hand Therapy and Burns and plastics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kate Attrill, Clinical lead therapist for burns and plastics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;kate.attrill@chelwest.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 0203 315 5680&lt;/p&gt;
